is still just a fake sword.

10
00:02:11,300 --> 00:02:11,950
[Wangquan]

11
00:02:13,430 --> 00:02:14,830
At Nangong's residence,

12
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:17,220
Zhang Zheng noticed something was amiss,

13
00:02:17,220 --> 00:02:18,550
but he didn't expose me.

14
00:02:19,430 --> 00:02:21,090
We'll deal with it as it comes.

15
00:02:21,460 --> 00:02:22,800
Don't worry, Young Master.

16
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:25,190
I'll forge a new sword as soon as possible.

17
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,620
The family masters

18
00:02:27,750 --> 00:02:29,550
are already waiting in the hall.

19
00:02:29,630 --> 00:02:31,280
Except for the Nangong family,

20
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:33,079
all the families have gathered.

21
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,430
Young Master Wangquan.

22
00:02:44,010 --> 00:02:45,910
[Yang Huanzhou, Master of the Clairvoyant Yang family, Yiqi Alliance]

23
00:02:48,690 --> 00:02:49,490
Mr. Fei.

24
00:02:52,030 --> 00:02:53,490
The Yiqi Alliance decree:

25
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:56,970
Forging swords with demon cores
will backfire on the sword masters,

26
00:02:56,970 --> 00:02:59,120
causing them to lose their mind.

27
00:02:59,190 --> 00:03:00,760
The harm is terrifying.

28
00:03:01,070 --> 00:03:02,280
From today onwards,

29
00:03:02,750 --> 00:03:04,210
within the Yiqi Alliance,

30
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:08,110
all families are forbidden to
forge swords using demon cores.

31
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:17,720
Wangquan Hongye.

32
00:03:18,710 --> 00:03:21,870
Don't think that just because you've banned
the use of demon cores in sword forging,

33
00:03:21,870 --> 00:03:24,680
the Nangong family has no other way
to deal with you.

34
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:27,840
We still have a long fight ahead of us.

35
00:03:39,690 --> 00:03:42,690
[Clairvoyant Yang Residence]

36
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,400
Grandfather.

37
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,150
Mu Xiaowu has been kneeling outside our house

38
00:03:46,150 --> 00:03:47,329
for a day and a night now.

39
00:03:47,329 --> 00:03:49,060
If he keeps kneeling like this,

40
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:51,000
I'm afraid something bad might happen.

41
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:51,780
Yitan.

42
00:03:53,030 --> 00:03:55,130
You don't need to get involved in this matter.

43
00:03:55,130 --> 00:03:57,470
[Yang Ying from the Clairvoyant Yang family, Yiqi Alliance]

44
00:03:55,930 --> 00:03:58,590
Even if our Yang family
has fallen on hard times,

45
00:03:58,710 --> 00:04:00,310
we are still descendants of a noble family.

46
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:02,150
It's that aunt of yours

47
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:04,870
who shamelessly did such a foolish thing

48
00:04:05,690 --> 00:04:07,950
and insisted that I agree to their marriage.

49
00:04:07,950 --> 00:04:09,440
Let her dream on.

50
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,080
Grandfather.

51
00:04:12,430 --> 00:04:14,840
Do you really think Aunt cares about

52
00:04:15,320 --> 00:04:17,610
being a descendant of a noble family?

53
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:20,800
Yitan!

54
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:22,450
What kind of talk is that?

55
00:04:22,450 --> 00:04:23,510
What your aunt has ruined

56
00:04:23,510 --> 00:04:25,070
is the reputation of our Yang family.

57
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:27,280
It's you, Yitan, who will be
affected by this.

58
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:28,090
Yang Ying.

59
00:04:28,930 --> 00:04:30,150
Get a midwife here

60
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:32,890
and get rid of that bastard in Yan's belly.

61
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,680
Yes.

62
00:04:33,980 --> 00:04:34,980
Stop right there.

63
00:04:38,380 --> 00:04:39,550
I'd like to see

64
00:04:39,610 --> 00:04:41,940
who dares to lay a finger on my aunt.

65
00:04:42,190 --> 00:04:42,800
You...

66
00:04:44,030 --> 00:04:45,560
If you want to agree to this marriage,

67
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,020
it'll be over my dead body!

68
00:04:49,330 --> 00:04:50,600
Father, don't be angry.

69
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:52,230
Yitan, watch your words!

70
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:55,050
Your grandfather is too old to handle such anger.

71
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:57,630
Fine.

72
00:04:59,909 --> 00:05:02,310
Then I'll go kneel with Mu Xiaowu right now,

73
00:05:02,630 --> 00:05:05,290
until you agree to this marriage, Grandfather.

74
00:05:08,060 --> 00:05:08,920
Please calm down, Father.

75
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:09,920
Don't be angry.

76
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:31,600
Why are you doing this?

77
00:05:33,630 --> 00:05:35,830
Uncle, I'll kneel with you.

78
00:05:44,450 --> 00:05:48,640
[Clairvoyant Yang Residence]

79
00:05:46,310 --> 00:05:47,070
Father.

80
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:49,680
It seems Yitan is serious about this.

81
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:56,690
Let them kneel.

82
00:06:00,330 --> 00:06:01,130
Father,

83
00:06:01,350 --> 00:06:02,230
let it go.

84
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:05,390
As the saying goes, "Not for the monk's sake
but for the Buddha's sake."

85
00:06:05,390 --> 00:06:07,190
In the three generations of our Yang family,

86
00:06:07,190 --> 00:06:08,190
apart from Yitan

87
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:09,650
and his deceased father,

88
00:06:10,390 --> 00:06:12,280
how many others are clairvoyant?

89
00:06:13,310 --> 00:06:15,190
Don't push Yitan

90
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,940
too far.

91
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:29,340
Yitan's marriage is the most decent cover

92
00:06:29,340 --> 00:06:32,490
for our Yang family's shame.

93
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:34,850
We can't afford any mishaps.

94
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:40,170
Master, Young Master Wangquan
is here to visit.

95
00:06:41,450 --> 00:06:42,280
Who?

96
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:50,200
Young Master Wangquan, what important matter

97
00:06:50,220 --> 00:06:51,950
brings you to our humble abode?

98
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:54,159
Master, you may have already heard that

99
00:06:54,159 --> 00:06:58,159
it was because I personally granted
a special pardon to your son-in-law

100
00:06:58,200 --> 00:07:00,430
that the Inspection Bureau released him.

101
00:07:00,430 --> 00:07:01,630
I have heard about it.

102
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,040
Young Master.

103
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:06,330
It truly is a noble act.

104
00:07:06,510 --> 00:07:08,240
I'm not the noble one.

105
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:11,070
It was just

106
00:07:11,570 --> 00:07:13,170
Xiaowu once saved my life by chance.

107
00:07:13,170 --> 00:07:16,430
I'm merely repaying the kindness.

108
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:21,680
He has never mentioned this matter before.

109
00:07:22,210 --> 00:07:24,600
So the truly noble one is

110
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:26,470
your great son-in-law here.

111
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:37,140
Xiaowu's family all perished in the flood.

112
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:39,610
So I, as the young master, took the liberty,

113
00:07:39,610 --> 00:07:41,180
to prepare these betrothal gifts.

114
00:07:41,180 --> 00:07:43,640
I also asked a highly respected Taoist priest

115
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:46,070
to pick an auspicious date,

116
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:57,140
[Mu Renzhi, Yang Yan]
[July 18th]

117
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:56,750
July 18th.

118
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,880
It will bring prosperity to the ancestors,

119
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:00,680
and good fortune in all matters.

120
00:08:00,730 --> 00:08:02,510
July 18th?

121
00:08:02,620 --> 00:08:04,560
Isn't that just a month from now?

122
00:08:04,580 --> 00:08:07,460
To be precise, it's a little over a month.

123
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:09,040
This period is neither too long

124
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,000
nor too short.

125
00:08:10,290 --> 00:08:11,690
It's just there won't be another

126
00:08:11,690 --> 00:08:15,140
auspicious date like this after that day.

127
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:19,210
What do you think, Master?

128
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:22,850
The date is well chosen,

129
00:08:22,880 --> 00:08:23,510
but...

130
00:08:23,510 --> 00:08:24,360
Excellent.

131
00:08:24,380 --> 00:08:26,020
Since you have no objections, Master,

132
00:08:26,020 --> 00:08:26,900
Xiaowu,

133
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:29,100
serve tea to your father-in-law.

134
00:08:38,390 --> 00:08:39,200
Master.

135
00:08:40,510 --> 00:08:43,080
If you agree to let Yan marry me,

136
00:08:43,510 --> 00:08:44,570
I, Xiaowu, promise

137
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:47,850
that I will dedicate the rest of my life

138
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:50,760
to ensuring Yan's happiness and security.

139
00:08:55,150 --> 00:08:56,910
If you want to marry my Yan,

140
00:08:58,690 --> 00:09:00,510
you must marry into our family

141
00:09:00,730 --> 00:09:02,890
and live with our Yang family.

142
00:09:15,020 --> 00:09:16,220
I, Xiaowu, will obey.

143
00:09:23,750 --> 00:09:26,900
Since the auspicious date was set by you,

144
00:09:28,630 --> 00:09:31,200
Young Master, I have a request as well.

145
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:32,660
On the wedding day,

146
00:09:33,290 --> 00:09:34,820
I will definitely be there.

147
00:09:35,510 --> 00:09:36,270
Good.

148
00:09:49,070 --> 00:09:50,030
Xiaowu.

149
00:09:50,050 --> 00:09:51,180
-Yan.
-How did it go?

150
00:09:53,340 --> 00:09:55,980
We did it. Our marriage is settled.

151
00:09:58,550 --> 00:09:59,550
My father agreed?

152
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:03,150
The wedding date is set for one month from now.

153
00:10:05,090 --> 00:10:05,930
That's great.

154
00:10:08,910 --> 00:10:10,840
Aunt, he knelt for too long.

155
00:10:10,860 --> 00:10:11,720
Go and rest now.

156
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:16,050
I, Xiaowu, will surely repay

157
00:10:16,050 --> 00:10:18,970
your kindness in the future, Young Master.

158
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,050
Hongye.

159
00:10:33,550 --> 00:10:34,750
Why did you come here?

160
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:38,180
You just found out about your aunt and Mu Xiaowu?

161
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:43,250
You know about my family's situation, Hongye.

162
00:10:44,700 --> 00:10:46,650
I've looked into Mu Xiaowu's background.

163
00:10:46,650 --> 00:10:47,910
He is indeed talented.

164
00:10:47,950 --> 00:10:49,270
After he joins the Yang family,

165
00:10:49,270 --> 00:10:50,700
he should become a great help to you

166
00:10:50,700 --> 00:10:53,560
in improving the Yang family's current situation.

167
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,550
Hongye, I-

168
00:10:55,550 --> 00:10:56,150
Alright.

169
00:10:57,270 --> 00:10:58,270
I'll be going now.

170
00:11:22,990 --> 00:11:25,320
Now that Yang Yan's matter is resolved,

171
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:27,050
your face is glowing, Huaizhu.

172
00:11:27,670 --> 00:11:30,080
Only when she and Xiaowu successfully get married

173
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:33,010
can this matter be considered completely resolved.

174
00:11:33,250 --> 00:11:36,450
Then where does this glow on your face
come from, Huaizhu?

175
00:11:38,870 --> 00:11:41,510
Could it be that since July 7th is approaching,

176
00:11:41,510 --> 00:11:43,240
it's the glow of anticipation?

177
00:11:43,750 --> 00:11:44,550
You remember

178
00:11:44,550 --> 00:11:45,910
the date quite clearly.

179
00:11:45,910 --> 00:11:46,790
Of course.

180
00:11:46,790 --> 00:11:48,270
That's my masked brother-in-law, after all.

181
00:11:48,270 --> 00:11:49,080
I'm

182
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,020
very satisfied with him.

183
00:11:50,020 --> 00:11:52,150
It can be said that it was love at first-

184
00:11:52,330 --> 00:11:55,390
No, it was love at first sight
on behalf of you, Huaizhu.

185
00:12:00,070 --> 00:12:01,390
Miss Huaizhu. Miss Qinlan.

186
00:12:01,390 --> 00:12:02,770
Senior Renfeng has returned.

187
00:12:02,770 --> 00:12:05,110
Master asked you to welcome him
in the front hall.

188
00:12:05,110 --> 00:12:05,820
Got it.

189
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:11,360
Master, during my trip down the mountain
to hunt demons this time,

190
00:12:10,040 --> 00:12:12,250
[Jin Renfeng, the eldest disciple of Divine Fire Villa]

191
00:12:11,450 --> 00:12:13,180
the people were very grateful.

192
00:12:13,410 --> 00:12:15,930
They specially prepared these treasures for you

193
00:12:15,930 --> 00:12:17,720
and insisted that you must accept them.

194
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:18,710
Renfeng.

195
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:24,500
These things are a token of their sincerity.

196
00:12:24,630 --> 00:12:26,030
You may accept them.

197
00:12:26,490 --> 00:12:27,820
However, in the future,

198
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:31,120
we shouldn't accept any more gifts.

199
00:12:31,270 --> 00:12:31,870
Father.

200
00:12:32,270 --> 00:12:32,840
Yes.

201
00:12:34,230 --> 00:12:35,680
Senior Renfeng, you're here.

202
00:12:35,680 --> 00:12:37,070
When did you arrive?

203
00:12:37,090 --> 00:12:38,780
I just returned to the villa.

204
00:12:38,980 --> 00:12:39,910
Senior Renfeng.

205
00:12:40,970 --> 00:12:41,640
Father.

206
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,430
Oh, right, Junior Huaizhu.

207
00:12:46,430 --> 00:12:49,740
During my trip down the mountain this time,
I thought of you often,

208
00:12:49,740 --> 00:12:51,290
so I specially prepared a gift for you.

209
00:12:51,290 --> 00:12:53,270
Do you like this hairpin?

210
00:12:57,580 --> 00:12:59,110
I appreciate your gesture.

211
00:12:59,110 --> 00:13:01,640
Thank you for your kindness, Senior Renfeng.

212
00:13:03,940 --> 00:13:05,200
The medicine is ready.

213
00:13:05,420 --> 00:13:06,820
I'll serve you to take it.

214
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,980
It seems that after so many years,

215
00:13:13,980 --> 00:13:16,310
someone still doesn't know Huaizhu well.

216
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:19,340
She doesn't like these gaudy, glittering objects.

217
00:13:21,290 --> 00:13:24,150
Give it to me. I'll go exchange it
for some nice food.

218
00:13:25,280 --> 00:13:28,100
Renfeng, you've just returned.

219
00:13:28,130 --> 00:13:30,330
Go back to your room and have a good rest.

220
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:33,440
Yes, Master.

221
00:13:40,150 --> 00:13:42,510
Even if you don't want to accept his pursuit,

222
00:13:42,510 --> 00:13:43,870
don't be so harsh.

223
00:13:44,510 --> 00:13:47,280
After all, he is your eldest senior.

224
00:13:47,300 --> 00:13:48,620
I understand that you value him highly

225
00:13:48,620 --> 00:13:50,550
because he's the posthumous son

226
00:13:50,570 --> 00:13:52,170
of an old friend of yours, Father.

227
00:13:52,170 --> 00:13:53,370
That's exactly why

228
00:13:53,670 --> 00:13:56,030
I need to be very clear about my attitude.

229
00:13:58,750 --> 00:14:00,000
Yes. Right.

230
00:14:00,670 --> 00:14:02,270
You have a point, Huaizhu.

231
00:14:02,830 --> 00:14:06,070
I won't interfere with whom my Huaizhu likes.

232
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:09,490
Take your medicine.

233
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:26,280
Huaizhu.

234
00:14:26,950 --> 00:14:28,950
I have all the patience in the world.

235
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:30,670
One day,

236
00:14:30,910 --> 00:14:32,550
you will be mine.

237
00:14:35,290 --> 00:14:38,870
[Wangquan Manor]

238
00:14:37,550 --> 00:14:39,080
Although Nangong Ye is dead, the Inspection Bureau,

239
00:14:39,080 --> 00:14:41,720
which has always been independent from the Yiqi Alliance,

240
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:43,670
is still in the hands of the Nangong family.

241
00:14:43,670 --> 00:14:46,150
The Nangong family's interests are deeply intertwined with
those of other noble families,

242
00:14:46,150 --> 00:14:47,750
making it difficult to shake their position for now.

243
00:14:47,750 --> 00:14:49,410
Young Master, you still need to take control of

244
00:14:49,410 --> 00:14:53,360
the Inspection Bureau, which can keep the noble families in check.

245
00:14:55,790 --> 00:14:57,550
On such a beautiful day,

246
00:14:57,670 --> 00:14:58,270
Hongye,

247
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,320
you and Mr. Fei shouldn't keep talking about

248
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:01,320
such unpleasant matters.

249
00:15:01,550 --> 00:15:02,680
I have something important to discuss with you.

250
00:15:02,680 --> 00:15:03,600
What is it?

251
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:05,320
Look.

252
00:15:06,530 --> 00:15:09,060
Choose one of these two outfits that you like.

253
00:15:14,490 --> 00:15:15,370
The left one.

254
00:15:16,420 --> 00:15:17,840
Alright, the left one.

255
00:15:17,840 --> 00:15:18,570
Eliminated.

256
00:15:18,750 --> 00:15:19,390
Alright.

257
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:21,520
You may leave now.

258
00:15:21,680 --> 00:15:23,610
I'll go attend to my duties as well.

259
00:15:27,860 --> 00:15:30,340
Indeed, this outfit suits you better.

260
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:31,510
Is my taste really that...

261
00:15:31,510 --> 00:15:32,390
Hopeless.

262
00:15:32,490 --> 00:15:35,000
But you have a good eye for people.

263
00:15:35,460 --> 00:15:38,530
Why don't you wear this outfit to the Bamboo Pavilion
by River Huai tomorrow?

264
00:15:38,530 --> 00:15:39,030
You...

265
00:15:40,400 --> 00:15:42,320
I noticed this morning that you glanced

266
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:44,050
at the scabbard several times.

267
00:15:44,390 --> 00:15:45,870
A beautiful day, a lovely scene,
and a charming person.

268
00:15:45,870 --> 00:15:47,030
The timing is perfect.

269
00:15:47,030 --> 00:15:48,650
So, take off your mask

270
00:15:48,670 --> 00:15:50,960
and tell her who you are.

271
00:16:06,310 --> 00:16:09,430
[July 7th]

272
00:16:31,660 --> 00:16:34,040
