00:29:28,770 --> 00:29:30,610
Eat more, talk less.

549
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:34,090
Well, humans are born with mouths.

550
00:29:34,420 --> 00:29:36,360
If we only eat and don't talk,

551
00:29:36,510 --> 00:29:38,710
how are we different from rice buckets?

552
00:29:42,620 --> 00:29:44,280
I'm not referring to you guys.

553
00:29:46,500 --> 00:29:48,560
Don't you agree, dear nephew Hongye?

554
00:29:50,200 --> 00:29:51,000
Indeed.

555
00:29:52,090 --> 00:29:54,030
Although you're the young master,

556
00:29:54,160 --> 00:29:55,920
Huaizhu is already spoken for.

557
00:29:55,920 --> 00:29:58,320
Don't even think about making a move on her.

558
00:30:01,350 --> 00:30:04,030
I wonder if you've all heard of

559
00:30:04,270 --> 00:30:05,640
the Mask Group?

560
00:30:09,960 --> 00:30:10,960
Never heard of it.

561
00:30:13,710 --> 00:30:14,960
As expected.

562
00:30:14,960 --> 00:30:17,900
A mundane creature like Young Master Wangquan

563
00:30:17,960 --> 00:30:20,640
surely has never heard of
such an extraordinary person

564
00:30:20,640 --> 00:30:22,110
as the Mask Group Leader.

565
00:30:22,310 --> 00:30:24,720
He's the one my sister has her heart set on.

566
00:30:27,350 --> 00:30:30,590
Anyway, some people are absolutely
incomparable to him.

567
00:30:32,110 --> 00:30:32,960
Huaizhu.

568
00:30:33,270 --> 00:30:34,800
You didn't peel the shrimp.

569
00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:42,110
How exactly are some people
incomparable to him?

570
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:47,350
The Mask Group Leader is chivalrous and righteous,

571
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:49,030
but some people

572
00:30:49,030 --> 00:30:50,240
are vindictive.

573
00:30:50,780 --> 00:30:52,460
Although the Mask Group Leader

574
00:30:52,460 --> 00:30:54,110
wears a mask

575
00:30:54,110 --> 00:30:55,510
and dresses simply,

576
00:30:55,750 --> 00:30:56,960
he

577
00:30:57,070 --> 00:31:00,280
exudes an air of elegance and charm.

578
00:31:00,310 --> 00:31:01,920
Unlike some people

579
00:31:01,960 --> 00:31:04,160
who are clearly trying too hard.

580
00:31:07,170 --> 00:31:09,420
Moreover, his swordsmanship is
better than yours,

581
00:31:09,420 --> 00:31:10,550
he's taller than you,

582
00:31:10,550 --> 00:31:11,920
and he has a slimmer waist.

583
00:31:11,920 --> 00:31:14,380
You have absolutely no chance with Huaizhu.

584
00:31:20,070 --> 00:31:21,530
Zui, why are you giggling?

585
00:31:24,740 --> 00:31:26,030
I think

586
00:31:26,070 --> 00:31:28,610
Qinlan has a point.

587
00:31:28,630 --> 00:31:30,830
I never thought Hongye would see this day.

588
00:31:30,830 --> 00:31:31,850
This deserves a nice drink.

589
00:31:31,850 --> 00:31:33,530
Yitan, go get some wine.

590
00:31:34,350 --> 00:31:35,810
It's midday. Don't drink.

591
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:36,590
Yes.

592
00:31:37,350 --> 00:31:39,830
Authority is meant to be rebelled against.

593
00:31:39,830 --> 00:31:40,810
Dear nephew Yitan,

594
00:31:40,810 --> 00:31:42,400
stand up and go get the wine.

595
00:31:51,850 --> 00:31:53,060
The fish is good.

596
00:31:53,090 --> 00:31:54,690
Let's eat. Enjoy the dishes.

597
00:31:56,580 --> 00:31:58,110
Some people

598
00:31:58,130 --> 00:32:00,330
are so mean to their own siblings,

599
00:32:00,610 --> 00:32:02,210
not even letting them drink.

600
00:32:02,230 --> 00:32:03,070
It seems to me that apart from

601
00:32:03,070 --> 00:32:04,790
having the hyphenated name Wangquan,

602
00:32:04,790 --> 00:32:06,050
he has no other merits.

603
00:32:08,590 --> 00:32:10,750
Forget it. I'll stop talking. Let's eat.

604
00:32:10,750 --> 00:32:13,080
Come on, I'll propose a toast to everyone.

605
00:32:13,190 --> 00:32:14,290
Right. Come on.

606
00:32:14,340 --> 00:32:16,110
One glass for friendship, two for affection,

607
00:32:16,110 --> 00:32:17,590
and three make good friends.

608
00:32:17,590 --> 00:32:18,550
Cheers.

609
00:32:18,550 --> 00:32:19,010
Cheers.

610
00:32:28,270 --> 00:32:29,030
Look at you.

611
00:32:34,920 --> 00:32:36,160
Dear nephew Yitan.

612
00:32:36,550 --> 00:32:39,070
So what Qinlan meant during the meal

613
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:41,270
was to declare the Mask Group Leader's allegiance

614
00:32:41,270 --> 00:32:43,880
and tell Hongye not to have any delusions?

615
00:32:44,000 --> 00:32:45,730
That's what she meant, indeed.

616
00:32:46,840 --> 00:32:48,900
But aren't we of the same generation?

617
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:50,830
That's not important.

618
00:32:50,830 --> 00:32:53,550
What's important is that
once the wedding is over,

619
00:32:53,550 --> 00:32:55,550
it'll be hard for Hongye
to have another chance.

620
00:32:55,550 --> 00:32:57,030
With Miss Qinlan around,

621
00:32:57,050 --> 00:32:58,380
it is indeed difficult.

622
00:32:58,650 --> 00:33:00,660
We need to make a plan.

623
00:33:00,760 --> 00:33:01,670
What plan?

624
00:33:02,160 --> 00:33:03,240
Early tomorrow morning,

625
00:33:03,240 --> 00:33:06,790
Miss Dongfang will go to Ruyi Pavilion
to purchase jewelry.

626
00:33:06,810 --> 00:33:07,810
And then?

627
00:33:07,840 --> 00:33:10,490
Then we'll arrange for Hongye and Miss Dongfang

628
00:33:10,490 --> 00:33:12,350
to have a destined encounter.

629
00:33:12,380 --> 00:33:13,310
Attention here.

630
00:33:13,350 --> 00:33:17,480
We must elevate Hongye's image of
being free-spirited and unrestrained.

631
00:33:17,750 --> 00:33:18,750
I'll do as you say.

632
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:27,790
What's wrong?

633
00:33:27,960 --> 00:33:28,960
It's nothing, really.

634
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:29,960
It's just I heard that you particularly like

635
00:33:29,960 --> 00:33:31,960
candied hawthorn, Qinlan,

636
00:33:31,960 --> 00:33:34,160
so I specially bought you a stick.

637
00:33:38,520 --> 00:33:41,000
I didn't expect that you Wangquan family

638
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:42,510
would be so considerate.

639
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:43,830
Thanks.

640
00:33:53,110 --> 00:33:54,590
This candied hawthorn stick should be enough

641
00:33:54,590 --> 00:33:56,450
to make her sleep for a whole noon.

642
00:33:56,960 --> 00:33:58,420
How's it going on your end?

643
00:33:58,550 --> 00:34:00,110
Miss Dongfang has already left.

644
00:34:00,110 --> 00:34:01,030
What about Hongye?

645
00:34:01,030 --> 00:34:02,350
I told Hongye that my grandfather wanted

646
00:34:02,350 --> 00:34:04,570
to have a heart-to-heart talk with him,

647
00:34:04,640 --> 00:34:06,550
so he immediately ran away.

648
00:34:06,590 --> 00:34:08,110
He was going to Ruyi Pavilion
to see Fifth Sister.

649
00:34:08,110 --> 00:34:09,360
As expected of you, Yitan.

650
00:34:09,360 --> 00:34:10,630
Your timing is perfect.

651
00:34:10,630 --> 00:34:11,159
Let's go.

652
00:34:27,449 --> 00:34:28,310
How's it going?

653
00:34:29,199 --> 00:34:31,199
Miss Dongfang has already arrived.

654
00:34:31,780 --> 00:34:32,639
What about you?

655
00:34:32,679 --> 00:34:34,550
Have you arranged the person we need?

656
00:34:34,550 --> 00:34:35,730
It's all been arranged.

657
00:34:35,730 --> 00:34:39,270
Look, that Taoist priest will stop Miss Dongfang

658
00:34:39,350 --> 00:34:40,679
and ask her to draw a fortune stick.

659
00:34:40,679 --> 00:34:41,880
Miss, please wait.

660
00:34:41,100 --> 00:34:46,520
[Nanhu Inn]

661
00:34:43,030 --> 00:34:45,110
I see a peach blossom flush on your face,

662
00:34:45,110 --> 00:34:46,909
as if your love star is in motion.

663
00:34:47,860 --> 00:34:50,630
I have iron fortune sticks here
that can determine love fates,

664
00:34:50,630 --> 00:34:52,630
but they only work for those
destined to be together.

665
00:34:52,630 --> 00:34:55,230
Miss, would you like to have your fortune told?

666
00:34:55,230 --> 00:34:56,280
[Nanhu Inn]

667
00:34:55,690 --> 00:34:56,360
Miss.

668
00:34:56,380 --> 00:35:00,260
In this vast world, isn't there anyone
you care about?

669
00:35:11,960 --> 00:35:14,610
Don't worry, no matter how she shakes it,

670
00:35:14,630 --> 00:35:16,840
she will only draw that destined fortune stick.

671
00:35:16,840 --> 00:35:19,020
It will fall at Hongye's feet,

672
00:35:19,040 --> 00:35:20,810
and only he can pick it up.

673
00:35:20,890 --> 00:35:22,750
Here he comes. Here comes Hongye.

674
00:35:24,070 --> 00:35:25,080
Miss Huaizhu.

675
00:35:25,100 --> 00:35:26,430
Young Master Wangquan.

676
00:35:30,510 --> 00:35:32,860
Huaizhu, why didn't you take me
shopping with you?

677
00:35:32,860 --> 00:35:33,840
Why is she here?

678
00:35:33,840 --> 00:35:34,960
I swear that candied hawthorn stick

679
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:36,760
could even knock you out.

680
00:35:38,720 --> 00:35:40,730
[Nanhu Inn]

681
00:35:39,110 --> 00:35:39,710
You dropped your fortune stick.

682
00:35:39,710 --> 00:35:41,040
Let me pick it up for you.

683
00:36:00,230 --> 00:36:02,320
You two are outstanding individuals,

684
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:03,920
truly chosen by heaven.

685
00:36:04,660 --> 00:36:07,590
You are destined to be together
in three lifetimes.

686
00:36:07,840 --> 00:36:09,360
You haven't even read what's written
on the fortune stick.

687
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:11,890
How do you know we're destined
to be together?

688
00:36:15,320 --> 00:36:17,510
Only bamboo conceals a golden blade.

689
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:20,230
With apricot, there's no need for plum.

690
00:36:20,400 --> 00:36:22,280
Forming a bond brings wealth and honor.

691
00:36:22,280 --> 00:36:24,740
Heaven grants its convenience.

692
00:36:24,880 --> 00:36:25,920
Miss, look.

693
00:36:26,260 --> 00:36:28,800
If this isn't heaven's choice, what is?

694
00:36:29,320 --> 00:36:32,030
This fortune stick is indeed
the best of the best,

695
00:36:32,030 --> 00:36:33,230
but as for the person,

696
00:36:33,790 --> 00:36:35,020
I'm not worthy.

697
00:36:36,960 --> 00:36:37,710
Let's go.

698
00:36:44,400 --> 00:36:46,830
How much did Wangquan Zui pay you?

699
00:36:46,850 --> 00:36:49,310
I don't understand what you're saying, Sir.

700
00:36:49,320 --> 00:36:51,510
But your destined romance

701
00:36:51,530 --> 00:36:53,400
requires the help of an object.

702
00:37:02,400 --> 00:37:03,840
Destined romance.

703
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:05,430
Aided by an object.

704
00:37:05,550 --> 00:37:07,150
Destined romance.

705
00:37:07,230 --> 00:37:09,230
Aided by an object.

706
00:37:12,620 --> 00:37:14,700
There are a lot of fun things up ahead.

707
00:37:14,720 --> 00:37:16,140
Did you bring the Wind and Rain Talisman
with you?

708
00:37:16,140 --> 00:37:17,230
Rest assured.

709
00:37:23,670 --> 00:37:24,960
It's going to rain. Let's hurry back.

710
00:37:24,960 --> 00:37:25,580
Okay.

711
00:37:32,280 --> 00:37:33,630
Destined romance.

712
00:37:33,650 --> 00:37:34,980
Aided by an object.

713
00:37:38,000 --> 00:37:39,600
What talisman did you bring?

714
00:38:19,290 --> 00:38:21,120
Dear nephew Hongye.

715
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:24,510
This rain is really well-timed.

716
00:38:24,710 --> 00:38:27,510
That fortune stick also fell
in such a strange way.

717
00:38:27,590 --> 00:38:30,590
And that person who tried to drug me
with the candied hawthorn stick.

718
00:38:30,590 --> 00:38:32,510
How low.

719
00:38:32,540 --> 00:38:33,350
Qinlan.

720
00:38:34,580 --> 00:38:35,330
Let's go.

721
00:38:35,360 --> 00:38:36,660
We have important matters to attend to.

722
00:38:36,660 --> 00:38:37,220
Coming.

723
00:38:51,590 --> 00:38:55,050
It's alright, you don't need to
take responsibility for this.

724
00:38:56,350 --> 00:38:57,370
Next,

725
00:38:58,320 --> 00:38:59,880
are Hongye and Miss Dongfang

726
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:01,210
going to Ruyi Pavilion?

727
00:39:04,400 --> 00:39:05,250
Ruyi Pavilion.

728
00:39:05,250 --> 00:39:07,060
Right. Let's go to Ruyi Pavilion right away.

729
00:39:07,060 --> 00:39:07,790
Okay.

730
00:39:10,410 --> 00:39:12,330
[Ruyi Pavilion]

731
00:39:10,650 --> 00:39:13,910
These are all the latest designs
of the Qingmu's this year.

732
00:39:14,180 --> 00:39:16,910
Please feel free to browse and select, everyone.

733
00:39:23,890 --> 00:39:28,870
[Qingmu Yuan, the Mask Group's Side]

734
00:39:31,960 --> 00:39:32,840
Miss Qingmu.

735
00:39:33,010 --> 00:39:35,740
The guest I'm expecting should be arriving soon.

736
00:39:36,070 --> 00:39:37,150
Is everything ready?

737
00:39:37,150 --> 00:39:38,000
Yes.

738
00:39:38,110 --> 00:39:39,040
All in position.

739
00:39:41,510 --> 00:39:43,720
Miss Qingmu, look.

740
00:39:55,320 --> 00:39:56,650
Young Master Wangquan?

741
00:39:59,320 --> 00:40:00,720
Young Master Wangquan!

742
00:40:10,150 --> 00:40:11,280
Where did this young gentleman come from?

743
00:40:11,280 --> 00:40:12,730
He's so handsome and elegant.

744
00:40:12,730 --> 00:40:13,800
Indeed he is.

745
00:40:13,800 --> 00:40:16,870
This is Wangquan Hongye, Young Master
of the Yiqi Alliance.

746
00:40:16,870 --> 00:40:19,670
I didn't expect Wangquan Hongye
to be so handsome.

747
00:40:20,510 --> 00:40:22,070
He's stolen my heart in the blink of an eye.

748
00:40:22,070 --> 00:40:23,400
These ladies

749
00:40:23,400 --> 00:40:26,430
can actually see past Young Master's
disheveled appearance

750
00:40:26,430 --> 00:40:28,810
and observe his unique celestial charm.

751
00:40:29,320 --> 00:40:30,850
That's really impressive.

752
00:40:38,560 --> 00:40:39,890
Young Master Wangquan.

753
00:40:40,210 --> 00:40:42,290
The items you ordered have all arrived.

754
00:40:42,290 --> 00:40:43,750
Please follow me to the second floor
to take a look.
